> Or setup a rule for that person that any emails going to Deleted get 
> copied to Trash Can 2. As it will just be a folder, there will be no 
> option to empty Deleted folder on exiting Outlook. Have one of 
> Nicolas' scripts running to automatically delete files from the folder 
> Trash Can 2 when they are older than one month. This way the user can 
> copy files from the Trash Can 2 folder to retrieve deleted files.
>
> I know it's a little extreme and hard work to setup, but geez it's 
